page.title: 10A 9 YEAR OLDS DAY
page.content: I got up at 9.00.and my mum got my breakfast I had toast.I got washed and dressed and went to call for my friend. We played skipping.We sang songs and played with a puppy called Pip.At 1.00 I went in for my lunch.I had peas,chips and meat.After lunch I went to Minehead with my mum and picked up Michelle Pearse.When we got back we played at hop_scotch.We had tea at 6.00 We had fish and potatoes. Then we took Michelle home.When we came back I watched television.At 9.00 it was my bedtime.
